OL,3,CRestaurant in Reading opened its doors
OL,4,Cto those most in need on Christmas Day
OL,6,FA restaurant in Reading partnered with
OL,7,Fa local charity, Sadaka, to open its
OL,8,Fdoors to those in need on Christmas
OL,9,FDay.
OL,11,FManzanos on Oxford Road welcomed
OL,12,Faround 50 people with a meal and some
OL,13,Fsweet treats throughout the afternoon.
OL,15,FThe charity Sadaka is a non-profit
OL,16,Forganisation who support people facing
OL,17,Ffinancial hardship, homelessness or
OL,18,Fsocial isolation.
