OL,3,CRestaurant in Reading opened its doors
OL,4,Cto those most in need on Christmas Day
OL,6,FGift packs, with female sanitary
OL,7,Fproducts, were also gifted to the
OL,8,Fwomen in attendance thanks to Project
OL,9,FSalama, an organisation who support
OL,10,Findividuals to live a life free from
OL,11,Fabuse.
OL,13,FSadaka trustee, Shazia Fazal, said:
OL,14,F"Christmas is a time when hardship
OL,15,Ffeels heavier for many of the people
OL,16,Fwe support.
OL,18,F"At Sadaka, our mission has always
OL,19,Fbeen to give without judgement and
OL,20,Fseeing the community come together
OL,21,Ftoday reminds us why that matters.
