OL,3,CRestaurant in Reading opened its doors
OL,4,Cto those most in need on Christmas Day
OL,6,F"A warm meal, a friendly conversation,
OL,7,Fa moment of dignity ` these things can
OL,8,Fmake all the difference.
OL,10,F"We're incredibly grateful to everyone
OL,11,Fwho helped make this day special for
OL,12,Fthose who needed it most."
OL,14,FManzano's owner, Asam Aziz, said his
OL,15,Ffaith was a driving force in promoting
OL,16,Fthe festive feast initiative.
OL,18,FHe said: "You may ask why we are doing
OL,19,Fthis. In our faith, feeding people is
OL,20,Fa big deal.
