OL,3,CRestaurant in Reading opened its doors
OL,4,Cto those most in need on Christmas Day
OL,6,F"The Prophet Muhammad, Peace Be Upon
OL,7,FHim, said the best of you are those
OL,8,Fwho feed others.
OL,10,F"With austerity at an all-time high
OL,11,Fand many families struggling just to
OL,12,Fget by, we felt it was important to
OL,13,Fcreate a space where everyone is
OL,14,Fwelcome ` regardless of race,
OL,15,Fbackground or religion."
